    (CommitCA( S, 'Human' ) @ #k) ⇒
    (∃ D #i #j #s.
      ((((Sstart( S ) @ #i) ∧ (D( D ) @ #j)) ∧ (#i < #j)) ∧ (#j < #k)) ∧
      (Device( 'Human', D ) @ #s))"
